<section>
  <title>Assignment</title>
  <introduction>
<p>
This project is similar to the Data Acquisition project only you must use method 5 to save time and button presses to a text file. You must then plot the button presses as a function of time. Remember to add x and y labels to all figures.
</p>
  </introduction>

<xi:include href="./assignment_directions.ptx"/>

<subsection>
<title>Specific Directions</title>
<ol>
<li><p>Include a screenshot (entire computer screen) of your SD card open and mounted on your computer with your data file in it - 20%</p></li>
<li><p>Include a snippet (5 lines) of your data file - 20%</p></li>
<li><p>Include a plot of your button presses with time on the x-axis and button presses on the y-axis (no screenshots) - 40%</p></li>
</ol>

</subsection>
